article.description: — Mekhi Lairy had 25 points and Miami (Ohio) beat Little Rock 80-67 on Saturday.
article.headline: Lairy scores 25 as Miami (OH) defeats Little Rock 80-67
article.linkText: Lairy scores 25 as Miami (OH) defeats Little Rock 80-67
article.story: OXFORD, Ohio -- — Mekhi Lairy had 25 points and Miami (Ohio) beat Little Rock 80-67 on Saturday. Lairy also added five rebounds and six assists for the RedHawks (2-4). Billy Smith scored 18 points while finishing 6 of 10 from 3-point range, and added five rebounds. Anderson Mirambeaux was 3 of 7 shooting and 6 of 7 from the free throw line to finish with 12 points, while adding five rebounds, five assists, and three blocks. D.J. Smith led the way for the Trojans (2-5) with 18 points, four assists and three steals. Nigel John added 17 points for Little Rock. In addition, Myron Gardner had 12 points, six rebounds, five assists and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
